The Design System includes a variety of unique color themes. Each color theme is provided as its own CSS file. Design System themes affect contextual primary, secondary, tertiary, success, info, warning, and danger coloring of all child components.

@section {String} section Themes

@parentComponent {String} parentComponent Internal Products

@name {String} name Internal Products

@example {Code}

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://ds.gumgum.com/stable/theme-blue.css">

@renderMarkup {Boolean} renderMarkup false

@author {String} author Dan McKenna, Myles O'Connor

@tabTrigger {String} tabTrigger

@optionalClasses {Array} optionalClasses theme-blue.css,theme-darkblue.css,theme-darkgreen.css,theme-gold.css,theme-grayblue.css,theme-graygold.css,theme-grayred.css,theme-green.css,theme-orange.css,theme-orangegreen.css,theme-purple.css,theme-red.css,theme-vi.css

