The tooltip component, prefixed by <span class="gds-text--code">gds-tooltip</span>, is a small explanatory message that appears when hovering over an element. Tooltips require a 'data-tooltip' attribute containing their message.

@section {String} section Atoms

@parentComponent {String} parentComponent Tooltip

@name {String} name Tooltip

@example {Code}

<span class="gds-tooltip--right" data-tooltip="I am a tooltip!">
---]<button type="button" class="gds-button gds-button--primary">Button with tooltip</button>
</span>

@renderMarkup {Boolean} renderMarkup true

@author {String} author Myles O'Connor

@tabTrigger {String} tabTrigger gds-tooltip
@defaultClasses {Array} defaultClasses gds-tooltip
@optionalClasses {Array} optionalClasses gds-tooltip--top,gds-tooltip--right,gds-tooltip--bottom,gds-tooltip--left,gds-tooltip--primary,gds-tooltip--success,gds-tooltip--info,gds-tooltip--warning,gds-tooltip--danger,gds-tooltip--lg,gds-tooltip--always,gds-tooltip--no-animate,gds-tooltip--bounce

The avatar component, prefixed by <span class="gds-text--code">gds-avatar</span>, can display a user's photo, a brand's logo, or a flag icon for internationalization. The avatar can include a dropdown menu, which is meant to be shown when the avatar is clicked on. To show the dropdown menu, add the <span class="gds-text--code">gds-avatar--menu-open</span> class to <span class="gds-text--code">gds-avatar</span>  As with bubble menu and filter components, the button that invokes the avatar menu should contain a gds-bubble-button attribute with a value that points at some form of selector for the menu it corresponds to.

@section {String} section Molecules

@parentComponent {String} parentComponent Avatar

@name {String} name Avatar

@example {Code}

<div class="gds-avatar">
---]<div class="gds-avatar__image" data-gds-bubble-button="[data-gds-bubble-menu='avatar']" data-gds-active-class="gds-avatar__image--active">
---]---]<img src="https://ds.gumgum.com/images/ken.png" height="100%" alt="Ken Weiner" />
---]</div>
---]<div class="gds-avatar__menu" data-gds-bubble-menu="avatar">
---]---]<ul class="gds-avatar__menu-list">
---]---]---]<li class="gds-avatar__menu-list-item -ellipsis -p-h-3 -p-v-2">Ken Weiner</li>
---]---]---]<li class="gds-avatar__menu-list-divider"></li>
---]---]---]<li class="gds-avatar__menu-list-item -ellipsis"><a data-gds-bubble-closer class="gds-avatar__menu-list-link" href="#">Profile</a></li>
---]---]---]<li class="gds-avatar__menu-list-item -ellipsis" data-gds-bubble-closer ><a class="gds-avatar__menu-list-link" href="#">Settings</a></li>
---]---]---]<li class="gds-avatar__menu-list-divider"></li>
---]---]---]<li class="gds-avatar__menu-list-item -ellipsis"><a data-gds-bubble-closer class="gds-avatar__menu-list-link" href="#">Logout</a></li>
---]---]</ul>
---]</div>
</div>

@renderMarkup {Boolean} renderMarkup true

@author {String} author Dan McKenna, Myles O'Connor

@tabTrigger {String} tabTrigger gds-avatar

@optionalClasses {Array} optionalClasses gds-bubble__menu--menu-open,gds-avatar__image--active

The button-dropdown component, prefixed by <span class="gds-text--code">gds-button-dropdown</span>, is used for dropdown menus. To expand the dropdown menu, add the <span class="gds-text--code">gds-button-dropdown--active</span> class to <span class="gds-text--code">gds-button-dropdown</span>. Use the modifier <span class="gds-text--code">gds-button-dropdown--sm</span> for a smaller dropdown menu.

@section {String} section Molecules

@parentComponent {String} parentComponent Button-Dropdown

@name {String} name Button-Dropdown

@example {Code}

<div class="gds-button-dropdown" data-gds-dropdown>
---]<button type="button" class="gds-button-dropdown__button gds-button--primary" data-gds-dropdown-button>Dropdown Menu</button>
---]<ul class="gds-button-dropdown__menu">
---]---]<li class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-item"><a class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-link">Link</a></li>
---]---]<li class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-item"><a class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-link">Link</a></li>
---]---]<li class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-item"><a class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-link">Link</a></li>
---]---]<li class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-item"><a class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-link">Link</a></li>
---]---]<li class="gds-button-dropdown__divider"></li>
---]---]<li class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-item"><a class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-link">Link</a></li>
---]---]<li class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-item"><a class="gds-button-dropdown__menu-link">Link</a></li>
---]</ul>
</div>

@renderMarkup {Boolean} renderMarkup true

@author {String} author Dan McKenna

@tabTrigger {String} tabTrigger gds-button-dropdown
@defaultClasses {Array} defaultClasses gds-button-dropdown
@optionalClasses {Array} optionalClasses gds-button-dropdown--sm

